{"tid":2223760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"示威期間警長疑被膠枝打中 青年被控襲警","createTime":"2020-09-30T05:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T05:27:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47540d03ba183e5f1abf2ef871a904e4393499e3","tid":2223760,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:23:29.000Z","msg":"去年11月2日港島區原有多個獲發不反對通知書的集會，惟均被警方腰斬。警方當天在灣仔驅散示威者期間，有19歲青年疑以膠枝打向警員，警員以警棍還擊並制服青年。事隔多月，涉案青年被控襲警罪，案件今提堂。辯方申請押後案件，以便索取文件及法律意見，獲裁判官批准，其間被告獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/UIM76ZVEQFA4JLJH5BX4DVDSSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FUIM76ZVEQFA4JLJH5BX4DVDSSU%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=22a57bec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FUIM76ZVEQFA4JLJH5BX4DVDSSU%2F&h=46104603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/UIM76ZVEQFA4JLJH5BX4DVDSSU/</a>"},{"pid":"da42113542fb380887f543066850c9a3edef43b6","tid":2223760,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d22830bf9827cc947a0a8bab342da4e2d523bf","tid":2223760,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da42113542fb380887f543066850c9a3edef43b6","tid":2223760,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69737c027437f9d75c4360b04bbc15262b3def01","tid":2223760,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4d22830bf9827cc947a0a8bab342da4e2d523bf","tid":2223760,"uid":241504,"like":0,"di